properties.name: Heat Wave
properties.description:
Too hot to sleep; too hot to cook; too hot to run; too hot to trot; too hot to stop; too hot to handle. These are just some of the things that conventional wisdom tells us it is too hot to do.

While it may or may not be too hot to write a timely and coherent announcement (and for that we apologize), it is most certainly not too hot to go outside and ride a bicycle. So we suggest that you do exactly that, with us, tonight. If you would prefer to defy conventional wisdom and cook, handle or trot this evening instead, then, well, the choice is yours. But don't say nobody warned you.
